    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    The Secretary of State has reappointed James Chapman, Ian Rosenblatt, Virginia Tandy and Heather Lauder as Trustees of National Museums Liverpool.
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">James Chapman, Ian Rosenblatt, and Virginia Tandy have been reappointed by the Secretary of State for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport as Trustees of National Museums Liverpool for four years from 1 December 2020 to 31 November 2024. Heather Lauder has been reappointed by the Secretary of State for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport as Trustees of National Museums Liverpool for four years from 1 January 2021 to 31 December 2025.
</p>

  </div>
</div>

